\": \"As that milestone beckons, Landi said, Biles is benefiting from the work she does outside the gym to maintain her mental balance amid the pressure that comes with being considered the greatest of all time.\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1635, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that milestone beckons\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1455}, {\"ngram\": \"Landi\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental balance\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"all time\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's calm, she laughs, she's back to her sometimes goofy self that we had missed a few times,\\\" Landi told reporters during a pre-trials training day on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"self\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"Landi\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1739}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"a pre-trials training day\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I think this is where it shows\\u2026 she has a few tools that are personal to her, but that helps her stay calm and remember why she's here.\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few tools\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And how to think positive.\\\"\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1970, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Landi said she's seen Biles's confidence grow even since the World Championships last October.\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 2066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Landi\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles's confidence\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think even at Worlds she was confident, but I do not think it was where she is this year,\\\" Landi said.\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Worlds\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"Landi\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's just taken a little more time on that end.\\\"\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that end\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles said at nationals this month she was enjoying gymnastics without \\\"stressing or having any anxiety\\\".\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"nationals\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2256}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2295}, {\"ngram\": \"any anxiety\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Landi said she could see a difference compared to Biles' state at the trials for Tokyo.\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2421, \"end\": 2426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9997087977064186, \"rank\": 0.0002645976757592751, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Landi\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2345}, {\"ngram\": \"a difference\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2377}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles' state\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2402}, {\"ngram\": \"the trials\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think she's more prepared mentally than she was last time,\\\" Landi said.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Landi\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She feels the pressure obviously, but she knows she's ready.\\\"\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2566, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2579}]}]}"